### ============================================================
### WALLETS — Get Wallet, Initiate Charge, Request Deposit
### Base URL: http://localhost:8000
### All endpoints require a valid JWT access token
### ============================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000
@accessToken = PASTE_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE
@courierToken = PASTE_COURIER_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE


# ---------------------------------------------------------------
# GET MY WALLET
# ---------------------------------------------------------------

### [SUCCESS] Get My Wallet — authenticated user
GET {{baseUrl}}/wallets/my-wallet
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### [FAIL — Security] Get My Wallet — no token (401 Unauthorized)
GET {{baseUrl}}/wallets/my-wallet

###

### [FAIL — Security] Get My Wallet — forged JWT (401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/wallets/my-wallet
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiIxMjM0NTYifQ.FAKESIG


# ---------------------------------------------------------------
# INITIATE WALLET CHARGE (top-up via Paylink)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------

### [SUCCESS] Initiate Wallet Charge — valid amount (50 SAR)
POST {{baseUrl}}/wallets/initiate-charge
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount_sar": 50
}

###

### [SUCCESS] Initiate Wallet Charge — minimum valid amount (10 SAR)
POST {{baseUrl}}/wallets/initiate-charge
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount_sar": 10
}

###

### [FAIL — Validation] Initiate Charge — below minimum amount (400 Minimum 10 SAR)
POST {{baseUrl}}/wallets/initiate-charge
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount_sar": 5
}

###

### [FAIL — Validation] Initiate Charge — negative amount (400)
POST {{baseUrl}}/wallets/initiate-charge
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount_sar": -100
}

###

### [FAIL — Security] Initiate Charge — no token (401)
POST {{baseUrl}}/wallets/initiate-charge
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount_sar": 100
}


# ---------------------------------------------------------------
# REQUEST WALLET DEPOSIT PAYOUT (couriers only)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------

### [SUCCESS] Request Deposit — courier requests payout (100 SAR)
POST {{baseUrl}}/wallets/request-deposit
Authorization: Bearer {{courierToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 100
}

###

### [SUCCESS] Request Deposit — courier requests payout (50 SAR)
POST {{baseUrl}}/wallets/request-deposit
Authorization: Bearer {{courierToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 50
}

###

### [FAIL — Security] Request Deposit — customer tries to request payout (403 Couriers only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/wallets/request-deposit
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 200
}

###

### [FAIL — Security] Request Deposit — no token (401)
POST {{baseUrl}}/wallets/request-deposit
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 100
}

###

### [FAIL — Validation] Request Deposit — zero amount
POST {{baseUrl}}/wallets/request-deposit
Authorization: Bearer {{courierToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 0
}
